ygData.messageBody:
I found the answer last night! My factions are too high with the "good guys"
and too low with the corrupt guards. I can't go anywhere near the docks or
Fish's Ale areas without getting killed by the corrupt guards.

And, yes, High Elf (Paladins at least) can only have Tunare.
